       01  XZUGOTMY-CA.
           COPY  XZUGOTMY.

       01  XIJICOMM-CA.
           COPY  XIJICOMM.
      *   T/E변경고객정보관리
       01  XDJLB153-CA.
           COPY  XDJLB153.
      *   T/E변경고객정보조회
       01  XDJL4153-CA.
           COPY  XDJL4153.

